# radroots-app-core

Core application runtime primitives for Rad Roots app surfaces.

## Goals

- define stable app runtime and error interfaces for Rad Roots clients
- provide unified logging and network integration points for app surfaces
- keep app runtime behavior deterministic across supported targets
- expose reusable app primitives for higher-level Rad Roots crates

